data.definition: relating to or characteristic of Ethiopia or its people

data.definition: A breed of domestic cat originating in the United States, known for its sturdy build and short, dense coat.

data.definition: A domesticated cat of a breed developed by crossing the Asian leopard cat with a domestic cat, characterized by its distinctive spotted or marbled coat.
